d.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Badsector","CreatedById":118465,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-02T19:11:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably now you understand better, the cockpit rotate and the panels rotate for get the best position vs sun\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/yZohb/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2 axis and 3 rotations \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only problem i have to add 3 actions for the same part.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-02T19:41:06Z\u0022 title=\u002202/02/2016 07:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 2, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Badsector\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CobaltWolf","CreatedById":105588,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-06T15:48:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh! Very interesting part. So is the one solar module a dummy to get the rotation on the vertical axis?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Badsector","CreatedById":118465,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-06T15:51:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222396515\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022130961\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221454773714\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105588\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CobaltWol